{"type":"message","id":"48852d2a","parentId":"aa7c20cd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T02:54:09.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"GitHub Token 权限配置取决于你想让我做什么。常见场景：\n\n## 1. 读取公开仓库\n**不需要 Token** — 直接访问即可\n\n## 2. 读取你的私有仓库\n需要 **Classic Personal Access Token**：\n- `repo` — 完整仓库访问（私有+公开）\n- `read:org` — 读取组织成员（如果需要）\n\n## 3. 创建/修改仓库、提交代码\n- `repo` — 完整仓库控制\n- `workflow` — 修改 GitHub Actions 工作流文件\n\n## 4. 管理 Issues / PRs\n- `repo` 已包含\n- 或 Fine-grained Token 选择：\n  - Issues: Read/Write\n  - Pull requests: Read/Write\n  - Contents: Read/Write\n\n---\n\n## 推荐配置（最常用）\n\n**Classic Token**（简单）：\n```\n✓ repo\n```\n\n**Fine-grained Token**（更安全，推荐）：\n- 选择特定仓库\n- Repository permissions:\n  - Contents: Read and write\n  - Issues: Read and write\n  - Pull requests: Read and write\n\n---\n\n## 给我使用的方式\n\n1. 在 [GitHub Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens](https://github.com/settings/tokens) 创建\n2. 将 Token 存到环境变量或配置文件（如 `.env`）\n3. 告诉我 Token 的位置，或直接在需要时提供\n\n**你现在想让我做什么？** 我可以根据具体需求告诉你最小权限配置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":9008,"output":327,"cacheRead":5376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773716036114}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3b20c4e","parentId":"48852d2a","timestamp":"2026-03-17T02:57:54.613Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 10:57 GMT+8] Repository access"}],"timestamp":1773716274612}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3e3622d","parentId":"b3b20c4e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T02:58:04.370Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Repository access 需要以下权限：\n\n## Classic Personal Access Token\n\n```\n✓ repo    (完整仓库访问，包括私有仓库)\n```\n\n## Fine-grained Personal Access Token（推荐，更安全）\n\n**Repository access**: 选择\n- `Only select repositories` → 指定具体仓库\n- 或 `All repositories`\n\n**Repository permissions**:\n| Permission | 级别 | 用途 |\n|-----------|------|------|\n| **Contents** | Read and write | 读取/修改代码、文件 |\n| **Issues** | Read and write | 管理 Issues |\n| **Pull requests** | Read and write | 管理 PR |\n| **Actions** | Read and write | 运行/管理工作流（可选） |\n| **Metadata** | Read | 自动包含，基础信息读取 |\n\n---\n\n## 创建步骤\n\n1. 访问 https://github.com/settings/tokens\n2. 选择 **Fine-grained personal access tokens** → **Generate new token**\n3. 设置 Token name、Expiration、Description\n4. 选择 Repository access（建议选具体仓库）\n5. 勾选上述权限\n6. 点击 **Generate token**\n7. **立即复制 Token**（只显示一次）\n\n---\n\n## 给我使用\n\n创建后，你可以：\n- 直接粘贴给我（会话内安全）\n- 或设置环境变量 `GITHUB_TOKEN`，告诉我变量名\n\n**需要我帮你操作仓库做什么？** 克隆、提交、创建 PR、还是其他？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":9139,"output":307,"cacheRead":5632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15078,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773716274612}}
{"type":"message","id":"4dc81883","parentId":"f3e3622d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T02:58:35.407Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 10:58 GMT+8] Public repositories\nRead-only access to public repositories.\n\nAll repositories\nThis applies to all current and future repositories you own. Also includes public repositories (read-only).\n\nOnly select repositories\nSelect at least one repository. Max 50 repositories. Also includes public repositories (read-only)."}],"timestamp":1773716315406}}
{"type":"message","id":"e277107b","parentId":"4dc81883","timestamp":"2026-03-17T02:58:54.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果只访问**公开仓库**，权限很简单：\n\n## Fine-grained Token 配置\n\n**Repository access**: \n- `All repositories` 或 `Only select repositories` 都行\n\n**Repository permissions**:\n```\nMetadata: Read    (自动包含，基础必需)\nContents: Read    (读取代码文件)\n```\n\n其他权限根据需求可选：\n- `Issues: Read` — 读取 Issues\n- `Pull requests: Read` — 读取 PR\n\n---\n\n## 更简单的选择\n\n其实访问**公开仓库不需要任何 Token**，直接就能读。\n\n**什么情况下需要 Token？**\n- API 速率限制更高（无 Token 每小时 60 请求，有 Token 5000 请求）\n- 访问你的私有仓库\n- 需要写操作\n\n---\n\n## 推荐\n\n如果只是偶尔查询公开仓库 → **不用创建 Token**\n\n如果需要频繁查询或避免速率限制 → 创建 Fine-grained Token，只给 `Metadata: Read` 和 `Contents: Read` 即可\n\n**你的使用场景是什么？** 我可以判断是否真的需要 Token。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":599,"output":222,"cacheRead":14592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15413,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773716315407}}
