{"type":"message","id":"8cbe501d","parentId":"258ecd8d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:00:39.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，需要**写入权限**。配置如下：\n\n## Fine-grained Personal Access Token\n\n**Repository access**:\n- `Only select repositories` → 选择你的备份目标仓库\n\n**Repository permissions**:\n| Permission | 级别 |\n|-----------|------|\n| **Contents** | **Read and write** |\n| **Metadata** | Read（自动）|\n\n---\n\n## 创建步骤\n\n1. https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta\n2. **Token name**: `OpenClaw Backup`（或其他）\n3. **Repository access**: `Only select repositories` → 选你的仓库\n4. **Permissions** → **Repository permissions**:\n   - ✅ Contents: **Read and write**\n5. **Generate token** → **立即复制**\n\n---\n\n## 给我使用\n\n粘贴 Token 给我，或设置环境变量：\n\n```powershell\n$env:GITHUB_TOKEN = \"ghp_xxxxxxxx\"\n```\n\n然后告诉我：\n- **仓库地址**（如 `https://github.com/username/backup-repo`）\n- **备份内容路径**（本地哪个文件夹）\n- **上传到仓库哪个位置**\n\n我就能直接操作了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":374,"output":237,"cacheRead":15104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15715,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773716431467}}
