{"type":"message","id":"dff9f9e9","parentId":"177007e1","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:14:52.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是一个展示 OpenClaw Hub 面板的视频截图。从图中可以看到：\n\n**OpenClaw Hub 界面功能：**\n- **快速控制** — 进入 WebUI、重启、检查更新、故障修复、沙箱模式、停止服务\n- **系统状态** — CPU、内存、存储使用率\n- **智能代理矩阵 (Agent Matrix)** — 多个专业 Agent：\n  - `main` — 主代理\n  - `coder` — 编程助手\n  - `researcher` — 研究助手\n  - `evolution` — 进化/学习\n  - `sysadmin` — 系统管理\n  - `coordinator` — 协调器\n  - `security` — 安全\n  - `wechat` — 微信集成\n  - `analyst` — 分析\n  - `ppt-writer` — PPT 生成\n  - `vision` — 视觉\n\n**视频信息：**\n- 作者：@Jason\n- 标题：手搓 openclaw 面板，管理多只龙虾更简单\n- 热点：OpenClaw 实测体验（29.2万人在看）\n\n---\n\n您是想：\n1. **安装/配置类似的 OpenClaw Hub 面板？**\n2. **了解如何管理多个 Agent？**\n3. **其他问题？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":3747,"output":283,"cacheRead":26368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30398,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773717281629}}
