      | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | Peekaboo CLI.                                 |                    |\n| ✗ missing | 🔊 sag                              | ElevenLabs text-to-speech with mac-style say  | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | UX.                                           |                    |\n| ✗ missing | 📜 session-logs                     | Search and analyze your own session logs      | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | (older/parent conversations) using jq.        |                    |\n| ✗ missing | 🔉 sherpa-onnx-tts                  | Local text-to-speech via sherpa-onnx          | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | (offline, no cloud)                           |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 skill-creator                    | Create, edit, improve, or audit AgentSkills.  | openclaw-bundled   |\n|           |                                     | Use when creating a new skill from scratch    |                    |\n|           |                                     | or when asked to improve, review, audit,      |                    |\n|           |                                     | tidy up, or clean up an existing skill or     |                    |\n|           |                                     | SKILL.md file. Also use when editing or       |                    |\n|           |                                     | restructuring a skill directory (moving       |                    |\n|           |                                     | files to references/ or scripts/, removing    |                    |\n|           |                                     | stale content, validating against the         |                    |\n|           |                                     | AgentSkills spec). Triggers on phrases like   |                    |\n|           |         