{"type":"message","id":"2836d652","parentId":"284cf72c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:15:41.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据我的了解，视频中的 \"OpenClaw Hub\" 面板是**第三方社区开发的工具**，不是官方功能。目前官方 OpenClaw 主要提供：\n\n1. **CLI 命令行界面** — 您现在正在使用的\n2. **WebUI** — 基础 Web 界面\n3. **多种 Agent 类型** — 通过配置实现\n\n---\n\n## 可选方案\n\n### 方案 1: 配置多个 Agent（推荐）\n\nOpenClaw 支持配置多个专用 Agent，类似视频中的矩阵：\n\n```bash\n# 查看当前配置\nopenclaw config get agents\n\n# 编辑配置添加多个 Agent\nopenclaw config edit\n```\n\n配置示例（`~/.openclaw/config.json`）：\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"main\": { \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\" },\n    \"coder\": { \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\", \"thinking\": true },\n    \"researcher\": { \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\" },\n    \"sysadmin\": { \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\" }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 方案 2: 使用官方 WebUI\n\n```bash\nopenclaw webui\n```\n\n### 方案 3: 寻找/开发 Hub 面板\n\n视频中的面板可能是：\n- **ClawHub 上的社区项目**\n- **用户自行开发的界面**\n\n让我搜索一下是否有相关项目："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:20","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npx clawhub search panel","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":7468,"output":340,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773717331493}}
