{"type":"message","id":"4a703854","parentId":"0d8cf8f7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:17:07.426Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我看到 OpenClaw 已经在运行，Dashboard 在 `http://127.0.0.1:18789/`。现在我来开发一个类似的 Hub 面板。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"sessions_spawn:26","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"开发一个 OpenClaw Hub Web 面板，功能要求：\n\n1. **界面设计**（参考视频中的样式）：\n   - 顶部：系统状态监控（CPU、内存、存储使用率）\n   - 中间：Agent Matrix 网格布局，显示多个 Agent 卡片\n   - 底部：快速控制按钮\n\n2. **Agent Matrix** 包含以下 Agent（按视频中的布局）：\n   - main（主代理）\n   - coder（编程助手）\n   - researcher（研究助手）\n   - evolution（进化/学习）\n   - sysadmin（系统管理）\n   - coordinator（协调器）\n   - security（安全）\n   - wechat（微信集成）\n   - analyst（分析）\n   - ppt-writer（PPT 生成）\n   - vision（视觉）\n\n3. **每个 Agent 卡片显示**：\n   - Agent 名称\n   - 状态指示器（在线/离线/忙碌）\n   - 快速操作按钮（启动、停止、重启）\n   - 点击可进入对话\n\n4. **快速控制区**：\n   - 进入 WebUI\n   - 重启服务\n   - 检查更新\n   - 故障修复\n   - 沙箱模式\n   - 停止服务\n\n5. **技术栈**：\n   - HTML + CSS + JavaScript\n   - 使用 OpenClaw 的 API 获取状态和发送命令\n   - 响应式设计\n\n6. **输出要求**：\n   - 创建目录：`~/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw-hub/`\n   - 生成 `index.html`、`style.css`、`app.js`\n   - 提供一个启动脚本 `start.bat`\n\n请完整实现这个 Hub 面板，确保界面美观、功能完整。","runtime":"subagent","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":300}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":1989,"output":481,"cacheRead":37888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40358,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773717415962}}
