{"type":"message","id":"8c56d56b","parentId":"ececd80b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:39:16.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看来 `openclaw agent` 命令不支持直接操作。让我检查正确的命令："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:70","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agent --help","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":331,"output":43,"cacheRead":63488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63862,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773718753807}}
{"type":"message","id":"b65e70e6","parentId":"8c56d56b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:39:18.322Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:70","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — I keep secrets like a vault... unless you print them in debug logs again.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line|feishu|openclaw-lark|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|matrix|bluebubbles|zalo|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1987,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — I keep secrets like a vault... unless you print them in debug logs again.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line|feishu|openclaw-lark|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|matrix|bluebubbles|zalo|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773718758318}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5e3344f","parentId":"b65e70e6","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:39:21.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"原来 `openclaw agent` 是用来发送消息的，不是用来管理 Agent 的。OpenClaw 没有直接的 Agent 管理命令。让我修改 server.py 使用正确的方式来管理 Agent："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:71","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"D:\\openclaw-hub\\server.py","offset":240,"limit":80}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":723,"output":73,"cacheRead":63744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773718758323}}
{"type":"message","id":"02615ae5","parentId":"a5e3344f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:39:21.481Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:71","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \n        return jsonify({\n            \"success\": True,\n            \"data\": status\n        })\n        \n    except Exception as e:\n        return jsonify({\n            \"success\": False,\n            \"error\": str(e)\n        }), 500\n\n\n@app.route('/api/agents/<agent_id>/<action>', methods=['POST'])\ndef control_agent(agent_id, action):\n    \"\"\"控制 Agent（启动/停止/重启）\"\"\"\n    valid_actions = ['start', 'stop', 'restart']\n    \n    if action not in valid_actions:\n        return jsonify({\n            \"success\": False,\n            \"error\": f\"Invalid action. Valid actions: {', '.join(valid_actions)}\"\n        }), 400\n    \n    try:\n        # 构建命令\n        if action == \"restart\":\n            cmd = f\"openclaw agent restart {agent_id}\"\n        elif action == \"stop\":\n            cmd = f\"openclaw agent stop {agent_id}\"\n        else:  # start - 需要 -m 参数，使用默认消息\n            cmd = f\"openclaw agent start {agent_id} -m \\\"Agent started from Hub\\\"\"\n        \n        stdout, stderr, returncode = run_command(cmd)\n        \n        if returncode == 0:\n            return jsonify({\n                \"success\": True,\n                \"message\": f\"Agent {agent_id} {action} command executed successfully\",\n                \"output\": stdout\n            })\n        else:\n            return jsonify({\n                \"success\": False,\n                \"error\": stderr or stdout,\n                \"returncode\": returncode\n            }), 500\n            \n    except Exception as e:\n        return jsonify({\n            \"success\": False,\n            \"error\": str(e)\n        }), 500\n\n\n@app.route('/api/openclaw/status', methods=['GET'])\ndef get_openclaw_status():\n    \"\"\"获取 OpenClaw 整体状态\"\"\"\n    try:\n        stdout, stderr, returncode = run_command(\"openclaw status\")\n        \n        return jsonify({\n            \"success\": returncode == 0,\n            \"running\": returncode == 0,\n            \"output\": stdout,\n            \"error\": stderr if stderr else None\n        })\n    except Exception as e:\n        return jsonify({\n            \"success\": False,\n            \"running\": False,\n            \"error\": str(e)\n        })\n\n\n@app.route('/api/control/<action>', methods=['POST'])\ndef system_control(action):\n    \"\"\"系统控制操作\"\"\"\n    valid_actions = {\n        'restart': 'openclaw gateway restart',\n\n[122 more lines in file. Use offset=320 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773718761478}}
