{"type":"message","id":"0a0091d4","parentId":"8afbb601","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:56:32.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"实际上，OpenClaw 的 `--agent` 参数需要 Agent 已经在配置中注册。让我尝试另一种方式 - 直接在主配置中注册所有 Agent："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:133","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"sandbox\": {\n    \"enabled\": true\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"main\": {\n      \"name\": \"Main\",\n      \"description\": \"核心主代理\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\"\n    },\n    \"coder\": {\n      \"name\": \"Coder\",\n      \"description\": \"编程助手\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek/deepseek-coder\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/coder/agent\"\n    },\n    \"researcher\": {\n      \"name\": \"Researcher\",\n      \"description\": \"研究助手\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/researcher/agent\"\n    },\n    \"evolution\": {\n      \"name\": \"Evolution\",\n      \"description\": \"进化学习\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/evolution/agent\"\n    },\n    \"sysadmin\": {\n      \"name\": \"SysAdmin\",\n      \"description\": \"系统管理\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/sysadmin/agent\"\n    },\n    \"coordinator\": {\n      \"name\": \"Coordinator\",\n      \"description\": \"任务协调器\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/coordinator/agent\"\n    },\n    \"security\": {\n      \"name\": \"Security\",\n      \"description\": \"安全审计\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/security/agent\"\n    },\n    \"wechat\": {\n      \"name\": \"WeChat\",\n      \"description\": \"微信集成\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2.5\",\n      \"agentDir\": \"~/.openclaw/agents/wechat/agent\"\n    },\n    \"analyst\": {\n      \"name\": \"Analyst\",\n      \"description\": \"数据分析\",\n      \"model\": \"moonshot/kimi-k2