les.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat, feishu_chat_members\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages\n[plugins] feishu_search: Registered feishu_search_doc_wiki\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive_file, feishu_doc_comments, feishu_doc_media\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node\n[plugins] feishu_sheets: Registered feishu_sheet tool\n[plugins] feishu_im_bot_image: Registered feishu_im_bot_image tool\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image\n[plugins] Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, search, drive, wiki, sheets, im)\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_fetch_doc, feishu_create_doc, feishu_update_doc\n[plugins] feishu_oauth: Registered feishu_oauth tool\n[plugins] feishu_oauth_batch_auth: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773719805012}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f708cf8","parentId":"9542905c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:56:48.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 仍然没有识别其他 Agent。看来 OpenClaw 的 Agent 注册机制不是简单的配置文件。让我查看文档或尝试其他方法："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:137","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agent --agent coder --help","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":690,"output":59,"cacheRead":91648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92397,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773719805018}}
{"type":"message","id":"abdd0d6b","parentId":"5f708cf8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:56:50.586Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:137","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Your .env is showing; don't worry, I'll pretend I didn't see it.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line|feishu|openclaw-lark|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|matrix|bluebubbles|zalo|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1933,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Your .env is showing; don't worry, I'll pretend I didn't see it.\n\nUsage: openclaw agent [options]\n\nRun an agent turn via the Gateway (use --local for embedded)\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>               Agent id (overrides routing bindings)\n  --channel <channel>        Delivery channel:\n                             last|telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|line|feishu|openclaw-lark|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|matrix|bluebubbles|zalo|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon\n                             (omit to use the main session channel)\n  --deliver                  Send the agent's reply back to the selected channel\n                             (default: false)\n  -h, --help                 Display help for command\n  --json                     Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  --local                    Run the embedded agent locally (requires model\n                             provider API keys in your shell) (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>       Message body for the agent\n  --reply-account <id>       Delivery account id override\n  --reply-channel <channel>  Delivery channel override (separate from routing)\n  --reply-to <target>        Delivery target override (separate from session\n                             routing)\n  --session-id <id>          Use an explicit session id\n  -t, --to <number>          Recipient number in E.164 used to derive the\n                             session key\n  --thinking <level>         Thinking level: off | minimal | low | medium | high\n                             | xhigh\n  --timeout <seconds>        Override agent command timeout (seconds, default\n                             600 or config value)\n  --verbose <on|off>         Persist agent verbose level for the session\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"status update\"\n    Start a new session.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Summarize logs\"\n    Use a specific agent.\n  openclaw agent --session-id 1234 --message \"Summarize inbox\" --thinking medium\n    Target a session with explicit thinking level.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Trace logs\" --verbose on --json\n    Enable verbose logging and JSON output.\n  openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Summon reply\" --deliver\n    Deliver reply.\n  openclaw agent --agent ops --message \"Generate report\" --deliver --reply-channel slack --reply-to \"#reports\"\n    Send reply to a different channel/target.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773719810583}}
