{"type":"message","id":"b793d59c","parentId":"09839a18","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:04:40.283Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在刷新浏览器页面（按 Ctrl+F5 强制刷新），然后点击 Agent 的\"进入对话\"按钮测试。\n\n如果还是不行，请告诉我：\n1. 点击按钮后浏览器地址栏有没有变化？\n2. 有没有弹出通知消息？\n3. 浏览器控制台（F12）有没有报错？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":248,"output":67,"cacheRead":108544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773720276611}}
