{"type":"message","id":"d0e42406","parentId":"ef6aa459","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:07:26.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在刷新浏览器（Ctrl+F5），然后点击 Coder 的\"进入对话\"按钮。\n\n**注意：** 即使 URL 带上了 session ID，OpenClaw WebUI 可能仍然显示相同的界面，因为：\n1. 所有 Agent 共享同一个 workspace 和配置文件\n2. 系统提示词（SOUL.md、IDENTITY.md 等）是相同的\n3. 只有 models.json 不同（模型配置）\n\n**要真正区分不同 Agent，需要：**\n- 每个 Agent 有独立的 workspace\n- 或者每个 Agent 有不同的 IDENTITY.md 和 SOUL.md\n\n您想要我配置每个 Agent 有独立的身份和提示词吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":339,"output":144,"cacheRead":109568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110051,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773720439258}}
