{"type":"message","id":"4036fec1","parentId":"8a466bc8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:24:04.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在刷新浏览器（Ctrl+F5），然后点击 Coder 的\"进入对话\"按钮。\n\n**如果弹窗被拦截：**\n1. 浏览器地址栏会出现拦截提示，点击允许\n2. 或者手动访问 http://127.0.0.1:18789/\n\n**注意：** 即使打开了新窗口，OpenClaw WebUI 可能仍然显示相同的界面，因为所有 Agent 共享同一个 workspace 目录。要让每个 Agent 显示不同的身份，需要为每个 Agent 创建独立的 workspace。\n\n需要我为每个 Agent 创建独立的 workspace 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":286,"output":122,"cacheRead":116992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117400,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773721439721}}
