{"type":"message","id":"23fc0421","parentId":"7c454c23","timestamp":"2026-03-17T04:25:00.649Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我需要为每个 Agent 创建独立的 workspace，这样每个 Agent 都会显示不同的身份和性格。让我来实现："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"sessions_spawn:175","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"为每个 Agent 创建独立的 workspace。\n\nOpenClaw 的 workspace 位于 `~/.openclaw/workspace/`，包含：\n- SOUL.md - Agent 性格\n- IDENTITY.md - Agent 身份\n- USER.md - 用户信息\n- AGENTS.md - 工作指南\n- TOOLS.md - 工具配置\n- MEMORY.md - 记忆\n- HEARTBEAT.md - 心跳任务\n- skills/ - 技能目录\n\n需要为每个 Agent 创建独立的 workspace：\n\n目录结构：\n```\n~/.openclaw/workspaces/\n  ├── main/\n  │   ├── SOUL.md\n  │   ├── IDENTITY.md\n  │   ├── USER.md\n  │   └── ...\n  ├── coder/\n  │   ├── SOUL.md (Coder 的性格)\n  │   ├── IDENTITY.md (Coder 的身份)\n  │   └── ...\n  ├── researcher/\n  │   └── ...\n  └── ... (其他 Agent)\n```\n\n步骤：\n1. 创建 `~/.openclaw/workspaces/` 目录\n2. 为每个 Agent 复制 workspace 文件\n3. 使用 Agent 特定的 SOUL.md 和 IDENTITY.md（从 agents/<name>/agent/ 复制）\n4. 修改 Hub 的 server.py，在切换 Agent 时设置 `OPENCLAW_WORKSPACE` 环境变量\n\n需要创建的 Agent workspace：\n- main\n- coder\n- researcher\n- evolution\n- sysadmin\n- coordinator\n- security\n- wechat\n- analyst\n- ppt-writer\n- vision\n\n请创建所有 Agent 的独立 workspace。","runtime":"subagent","mode":"run","runTimeoutSeconds":300}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":213,"output":424,"cacheRead":117248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117885,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773721488516}}
