{"type":"message","id":"675a7ad5","parentId":"a21e6504","timestamp":"2026-03-17T05:21:17.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"根据搜索结果，这些 skill 都没有显示下载量，但可以从更新时间和版本号推断：\n\n| Skill | 版本 | 更新时间 | 功能 |\n|-------|------|----------|------|\n| **miliger-context-manager** | v2.2.4 | 2026-03-16 | 自动上下文管理，85%阈值触发 |\n| **context-preserver** | v1.0.1 | 2026-03-16 | 上下文保存、恢复、版本管理 |\n| **deus-context-engine** | v1.0.0 | 2026-03-16 | 对话和项目上下文维护 |\n\n**推荐安装 `miliger-context-manager`**：\n- 版本号最高（v2.2.4），说明迭代最多\n- 功能最全面（自动管理、无缝切换、监控使用率）\n\n要安装吗？\n```bash\nnpx clawhub install miliger-context-manager\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":420,"output":197,"cacheRead":146688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147305,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773724870495}}
