{"type":"message","id":"881857a6","parentId":"2e6d376b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T05:22:46.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这些 context 相关的 skill 都被标记为可疑。这是常见情况，因为上下文管理 skill 通常需要：\n- 访问文件系统保存/恢复状态\n- 调用外部 API\n- 执行代码\n\n**选项：**\n\n1. **强制安装**（推荐，如果您信任这些 skill）：\n   ```bash\n   npx clawhub install miliger-context-manager --force\n   ```\n\n2. **先审查代码**：\n   ```bash\n   npx clawhub inspect miliger-context-manager --files\n   ```\n\n3. **使用 OpenClaw 内置的 memory 功能**（已启用）\n\n您选择哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":165,"output":134,"cacheRead":147456,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147755,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773724960058}}
