{"type":"message","id":"d689d727","parentId":"14f542d3","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:06:45.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从日志可以看到飞书连接问题：\n\n```\n\"unauthorized conn=... reason=token_mismatch\"\n\"gateway token mismatch (open the dashboard URL and paste the token in Control UI settings)\"\n```\n\n**原因：** Gateway Token 不匹配\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. 打开 Dashboard: http://127.0.0.1:18789/\n2. 复制显示的 Token\n3. 在 Control UI 设置中粘贴该 Token\n\n或者让我检查当前 token 配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:56","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw config get gateway.auth.token","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":54878,"output":126,"cacheRead":24320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773734780509}}
