{"type":"message","id":"550a4b3e","parentId":"48e51902","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:22:47.693Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我试试 sessions_list 工具。我需要使用正确的命令。让我检查帮助："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:96","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw sessions --help","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":199,"output":41,"cacheRead":102144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102384,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773735763742}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9ffaf8e","parentId":"550a4b3e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:22:49.468Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:96","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Greetings, Professor Falken\n\nUsage: openclaw sessions [options] [command]\n\nList stored conversation sessions\n\nOptions:\n  --active <minutes>  Only show sessions updated within the past N minutes\n  --agent <id>        Agent id to inspect (default: configured default agent)\n  --all-agents        Aggregate sessions across all configured agents (default:\n                      false)\n  -h, --help          Display help for command\n  --json              Output as JSON (default: false)\n  --store <path>      Path to session store (default: resolved from config)\n  --verbose           Verbose logging (default: false)\n\nCommands:\n  cleanup             Run session-store maintenance now\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw sessions\n    List all sessions.\n  openclaw sessions --agent work\n    List sessions for one agent.\n  openclaw sessions --all-agents\n    Aggregate sessions across agents.\n  openclaw sessions --active 120\n    Only last 2 hours.\n  openclaw sessions --json\n    Machine-readable output.\n  openclaw sessions --store ./tmp/sessions.json\n    Use a specific session store.\n\nShows token usage per session when the agent reports it; set agents.defaults.contextTokens to cap the window and show %.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/sessions"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1768,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Greetings, Professor Falken\n\nUsage: openclaw sessions [options] [command]\n\nList stored conversation sessions\n\nOptions:\n  --active <minutes>  Only show sessions updated within the past N minutes\n  --agent <id>        Agent id to inspect (default: configured default agent)\n  --all-agents        Aggregate sessions across all configured agents (default:\n                      false)\n  -h, --help          Display help for command\n  --json              Output as JSON (default: false)\n  --store <path>      Path to session store (default: resolved from config)\n  --verbose           Verbose logging (default: false)\n\nCommands:\n  cleanup             Run session-store maintenance now\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw sessions\n    List all sessions.\n  openclaw sessions --agent work\n    List sessions for one agent.\n  openclaw sessions --all-agents\n    Aggregate sessions across agents.\n  openclaw sessions --active 120\n    Only last 2 hours.\n  openclaw sessions --json\n    Machine-readable output.\n  openclaw sessions --store ./tmp/sessions.json\n    Use a specific session store.\n\nShows token usage per session when the agent reports it; set agents.defaults.contextTokens to cap the window and show %.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/sessions","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773735769464}}
{"type":"message","id":"86997429","parentId":"d9ffaf8e","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:23:14.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我需要使用 `openclaw sessions --json` 来获取 JSON 格式的输出，然后解析它。让我修改脚本。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:97","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1","old_string":"# Get session list to check context usage\ntry {\n    $sessionsOutput = & openclaw sessions list --limit 5 2>&1\n    \n    # Parse session info - look for main session with token usage\n    $mainSession = $sessionsOutput | Select-String -Pattern 'main.*?(\\d+)k.*?(\\d+)k'\n    \n    if ($mainSession) {\n        $used = [int]$mainSession.Matches[0].Groups[1].Value\n        $total = [int]$mainSession.Matches[0].Groups[2].Value\n        $usage = [math]::Round(($used / $total) * 100)\n        \n        Write-Log \"Context usage: ${usage}% (${used}k/${total}k)\"\n        \n        if ($usage -ge $Threshold) {\n            Write-Log \"WARNING: Context usage ${usage}% exceeds threshold ${Threshold}%\"\n            \n            # Check memory files\n            $memoryDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\"\n            $memoryLite = \"$memoryDir\\MEMORY-LITE.md\"\n            \n            if (Test-Path $memoryLite) {\n                $content = Get-Content $memoryLite -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                $wordCount = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\n                Write-Log \"MEMORY-LITE.md: $wordCount words\"\n            }\n            \n            Write-Log \"ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\"\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Context usage normal: ${usage}%\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Log \"Could not find main session context info\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Log \"Error checking context: $_\"\n}","new_string":"# Get session list to check context usage\ntry {\n    $sessionsJson = & openclaw sessions --json 2>&1 | Out-String\n    $sessions = $sessionsJson | ConvertFrom-Json -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    \n    if ($sessions -and $sessions.Count -gt 0) {\n        # Find main session or first session with token usage\n        $mainSession = $sessions | Where-Object { $_.key -like '*main*' -or $_.key -eq 'main' } | Select-Object -First 1\n        if (-not $mainSession) {\n            $mainSession = $sessions | Select-Object -First 1\n        }\n        \n        if ($mainSession -and $mainSession.tokens) {\n            $used = $mainSession.tokens.used\n            $total = $mainSession.tokens.total\n            $usage = [math]::Round(($used / $total) * 100)\n            \n            Write-Log \"Context usage: ${usage}% (${used}/${total} tokens)\"\n            \n            if ($usage -ge $Threshold) {\n                Write-Log \"WARNING: Context usage ${usage}% exceeds threshold ${Threshold}%\"\n                \n                # Check memory files\n                $memoryDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\"\n                $memoryLite = \"$memoryDir\\MEMORY-LITE.md\"\n                \n                if (Test-Path $memoryLite) {\n                    $content = Get-Content $memoryLite -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                    $wordCount = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\n                    Write-Log \"MEMORY-LITE.md: $wordCount words\"\n                }\n                \n                Write-Log \"ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\"\n            } else {\n                Write-Log \"Context usage normal: ${usage}%\"\n            }\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Session found but no token info available\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Log \"No sessions found or could not parse JSON\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Log \"Error checking context: $_\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":551,"output":954,"cacheRead":102144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103649,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773735769469}}
