{"type":"message","id":"540095dd","parentId":"4dc326b5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:28:07.485Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"太好了！sessions_list 工具可以直接获取会话信息，包括 totalTokens 和 contextTokens。当前 main session：\n- totalTokens: 98638\n- contextTokens: 256000\n- 使用率：38.5%\n\n这远低于 60% 的阈值，所以是正常的。\n\n现在我可以创建一个更简单的监控方案 - 使用 OpenClaw 内置的 cron 系统，通过 agentTurn 来运行检查。但这需要创建一个专门的 skill 或使用现有的工具。\n\n实际上，最简单的方案是：\n1. 保持现有的定时任务（每 5 分钟触发一次系统事件）\n2. 当收到系统事件时，我（AI）会运行 sessions_list 检查\n3. 如果超过阈值，我会提醒用户\n\n但这样需要我持续运行，不太实际。\n\n更好的方案是创建一个简单的 Node.js 脚本或 Python 脚本来做监控，而不是 PowerShell。\n\n让我创建一个 Python 脚本，这样更可靠。✅ **当前状态：**\n- Main session 上下文使用率：**38.5%** (98,638 / 256,000 tokens)\n- 状态：正常（低于 60% 阈值）\n\n由于 PowerShell 脚本在 Windows 上有兼容性问题，建议：\n\n**方案 1：** 使用 Python 脚本（更可靠）\n**方案 2：** 手动监控（运行 `sessions_list` 查看）\n**方案 3：** 保持现有定时任务，我定期提醒\n\n您希望采用哪种方案？或者我可以创建一个 Python 版本的监控脚本。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":624,"output":314,"cacheRead":113152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114090,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773736077230}}
{"type":"message","id":"d2bf3ae7","parentId":"540095dd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:28:26.704Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 16:21:22 GMT+8] Exec completed (young-nu, code 0) :: 2026-03-17 16:21:22 - Could not parse context usage from status output\nSystem: [2026-03-17 16:25:57 GMT+8] 运行上下文监控。请执行：~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/miliger-context-manager/scripts/context-monitor.ps1\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 16:28 GMT+8] 方案1"}],"timestamp":1773736106700}}
{"type":"message","id":"8dd7d540","parentId":"d2bf3ae7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:28:48.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，创建 Python 版本的监控脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:111","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nContext Monitor for Windows\nMonitors OpenClaw session context usage and alerts when threshold is reached\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nimport json\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# Configuration\nTHRESHOLD = 60\nLOG_DIR = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace/logs\")\nLOG_FILE = os.path.join(LOG_DIR, \"context-monitor.log\")\n\ndef log(message):\n    timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n    log_line = f\"{timestamp} - {message}\"\n    print(log_line)\n    \n    # Ensure log directory exists\n    os.makedirs(LOG_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n    \n    with open(LOG_FILE, \"a\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        f.write(log_line + \"\\n\")\n\ndef main():\n    try:\n        # Run openclaw sessions command\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            [\"openclaw\", \"sessions\", \"--json\"],\n            capture_output=True,\n            text=True,\n            encoding=\"utf-8\",\n            errors=\"ignore\"\n        )\n        \n        # Parse JSON from stdout\n        data = json.loads(result.stdout)\n        \n        if data and \"sessions\" in data:\n            # Find main session\n            main_session = None\n            for session in data[\"sessions\"]:\n                if session.get(\"key\") == \"agent:main:main\":\n                    main_session = session\n                    break\n            \n            if main_session:\n                total_tokens = main_session.get(\"totalTokens\")\n                context_tokens = main_session.get(\"contextTokens\")\n                \n                if total_tokens and context_tokens:\n                    usage = round((total_tokens / context_tokens) * 100)\n                    \n                    log(f\"Context usage: {usage}% ({total_tokens}/{context_tokens} tokens)\")\n                    \n                    if usage >= THRESHOLD:\n                        log(f\"WARNING: Context usage {usage}% exceeds threshold {THRESHOLD}%\")\n                        \n                        # Check memory files\n                        memory_lite = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/MEMORY-LITE.md\")\n                        if os.path.exists(memory_lite):\n                            with open(memory_lite, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n                                content = f.read()\n                                word_count = len(content.split())\n                                log(f\"MEMORY-LITE.md: {word_count} words\")\n                        \n                        log(\"ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\")\n                    else:\n                        log(f\"Context usage normal: {usage}%\")\n                else:\n                    log(\"Main session found but no token info available\")\n            else:\n                log(\"Main session not found\")\n        else:\n            log(\"No sessions data found in JSON\")\n            \n    except json.JSONDecodeError as e:\n        log(f\"Error parsing JSON: {e}\")\n    except Exception as e:\n        log(f\"Error checking context: {e}\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":587,"output":756,"cacheRead":113664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773736106703}}
