{"type":"message","id":"a35f8e13","parentId":"0b61db25","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:36:33.227Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"网关目前运行正常。问题可能是：\n\n1. **重启时进程冲突**：旧进程没有完全停止，新进程无法启动\n2. **配置验证失败**：某些配置更改后，重启时验证失败\n3. **服务状态不同步**：Scheduled Task 状态与实际进程状态不一致\n\n让我创建一个更可靠的重启脚本，确保：\n1. 先完全停止服务\n2. 等待进程退出\n3. 再启动服务\n4. 验证启动成功\n\n或者，我可以建议使用 `openclaw doctor --fix` 来修复常见问题，或者检查是否有更好的重启方式。让我检查重启命令的问题。网关当前运行正常。问题分析：\n\n**自动重启失败原因：**\n1. **进程冲突** - 旧进程未完全停止，新进程无法启动\n2. **配置验证** - 某些配置更改后验证失败\n3. **服务状态不同步** - Scheduled Task 与实际进程状态不一致\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n让我创建一个可靠的重启脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:121","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"@echo off\nchcp 65001 >nul\necho [重启 OpenClaw Gateway]\n\n:: 1. 停止现有进程\necho 停止现有进程...\ntaskkill /F /IM node.exe /FI \"WINDOWTITLE eq openclaw*\" 2>nul\ntaskkill /F /IM node.exe /FI \"COMMANDLINE eq *openclaw*gateway*\" 2>nul\n\n:: 等待进程退出\ntimeout /t 2 /nobreak >nul\n\n:: 2. 验证端口释放\necho 检查端口 18789...\nnetstat -ano | findstr :18789 >nul\nif %errorlevel% equ 0 (\n    echo 警告: 端口仍被占用，强制释放...\n    for /f \"tokens=5\" %%a in ('netstat -ano ^| findstr :18789') do taskkill /F /PID %%a 2>nul\n)\n\n:: 3. 启动 Gateway\necho 启动 Gateway...\nstart /B cmd /c \"openclaw gateway start\"\n\n:: 4. 等待启动\ntimeout /t 3 /nobreak >nul\n\n:: 5. 验证状态\necho 验证状态...\nopenclaw gateway status | findstr \"RPC probe: ok\" >nul\nif %errorlevel% equ 0 (\n    echo [✓] Gateway 重启成功\n) else (\n    echo [✗] Gateway 启动失败，请检查日志\n)\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\restart-gateway.bat"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":699,"output":584,"cacheRead":117248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118531,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773736575511}}
